Class AbstractNews

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AddNews, News, RemoveNews

    public abstract class AbstractNews
extends AbstractCommand
implements org.bukkit.command.CommandExecutor
    AbstractNews subcommand handling class. Purpose of this class is to avoid duplicate code. Because there are multiple sub classes with different instances, field variables are declared static to save memory.
